334
00:35:19,520 --> 00:35:20,800
Go ahead.

335
00:35:20,800 --> 00:35:22,320
Wait until I can move again.

336
00:35:24,670 --> 00:35:25,950
Just stop.

337
00:35:25,950 --> 00:35:26,870
