340
00:35:30,670 --> 00:35:31,560
Whatever.

341
00:35:31,560 --> 00:35:33,000
We can only try our luck.

342
00:35:33,430 --> 00:35:34,360
Xie Meimei,

343
00:35:35,560 --> 00:35:36,600
