411
00:40:09,670 --> 00:40:11,470
The Demons are right behind.

412
00:40:22,600 --> 00:40:24,360
I’ve practiced the Palm my whole life

413
00:40:25,600 --> 00:40:26,920
but in the end,

414
00:40:27,230 --> 00:40:28,670
I’ve only mastered

415
00:40:28,670 --> 00:40:29,810
half of it.

416
00:40:40,710 --> 00:40:41,630
Let’s go.

